<text>[[Figure skating]] at the [[1932 Winter Olympics]] took place at the Olympic Center Arena in Lake Placid, New York. Three figure skating events were contested: men&#x27;s singles, ladies&#x27; singles, and pair skating. The competitions were held from Monday, 8 February to Friday, 12 February 1932. It was the first time the events were held indoors.

