<text>Figure skating at the [[1936 Winter Olympics]] took place at the Olympia-Kunsteisstadion in Garmisch-Partenkirchen, Bavaria, from 9 to 15 February 1936. Three figure skating events were contested: men&#x27;s singles, ladies&#x27; singles, and pairs skating.

