<doc id="980217" wikidata="Q305378" url="?curid=980217" title="Solid State Records">
<text>Solid State Records is a metalcore record label, an imprint of Tooth &amp; Nail Records. Unlike Tooth &amp; Nail, Solid State signs hardcore punk and heavy metal bands. Like Tooth &amp; Nail, Solid State is primarily a Christian label. However, it signed several bands with Christian members which don&#x27;t label themselves as Christian bands, including Stretch Arm Strong, Gwen Stacy, He Is Legend, the Famine, Training for Utopia, and the Agony Scene.

