<doc id="980223" wikidata="Q16212867" url="?curid=980223" title="Dave Perry">
<text>David Roy Perry (born 21 May 1966) is a British broadcaster who was co-commentator on the UK computer and video games television shows &quot;GamesMaster&quot; and &quot;Games World&quot;. Perry was most famous for walking off &quot;GamesMaster&quot;.

He was responsible for launching many games magazines, including &quot;Games World&quot;, &quot;Play&quot;, &quot;PowerStation&quot;, &quot;X-Gen&quot;, &quot;STATION&quot; and &quot;Mega Power&quot;. He has since opened a tattoo parlour named Revolver Tattoo Rooms.

